---
title: Pork Tenderloin and Root Veggie Tray Bake with Gravy
description: Nothing says comfort food like pan-roasted pork tenderloin and a hearty veggie medley of potatoes, carrots and squash. Served with a drizzle of a rich mustard sage gravy, this dish will have you licking your plate clean!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/filet-de-porc-et-legumes-racines-au-four-c854dd05.jpg
